    ActionExecutingFunctionFactory, ContributingActionFactory, DefaultActionContributionFactory, DefaultActionFactory, StaticMethodInvokingFunctionFactory

    public abstract class AbstractLibraryElement
extends Object
implements LibraryElement
    Reduces the effort it takes to implement subinterfaces of the library element interface.

      • injectFields

        protected void injectFields(Object injectable)
                     throws AluminumException
        Injects all of an object's fields that are annotated with @Injected. The following field types are supported:
        • The current configuration;
        • This library element's type.
        Subclasses may extend the list of supported types by overriding the addValueProviders method.
        Parameters:
        injectable - the object whose fields should be injected
        Throws:
        AluminumException - when the object's fields can't be injected
